{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the first and the last was always freezing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we, we swapped all night who is the first and went inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we wanted to turn, it was so narrow, we had to be on our side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we all had to turn in-- on the same moment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the food we got was in, in cheap wash basins, one basin for 10 women.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here we were, dirty, full of lice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had to put the hands in the wash basin to eat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I, I thought, if I'm here, I'm going to get out of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I just don't want to stay here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And because I was right on top, there were-- it was like horse barracks that had little slits on, on top where you could look out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one day, there was an awful commotion, and, and I, I looked out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was a soldier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was-- very thin women were running in front of him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, and he was behind them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And obviously, he wanted to take them to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were running all over the place, and he was shooting and screaming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And by that time, of course, we knew everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We knew about the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the smell of the-- of the chimney was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It, it just-- it's-- the stench is just awful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And at night, you saw the flames coming out.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
